highlights.text: Maan Meri Jaan by King is the highest new entry on Top Songs Pune at #45.
Daku by Chani Nattan and Inderpal Moga is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Pune, up 54 spots at #40.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Pune. Kesariya is the highest at #1.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Pune the longest, at 55 weeks straight.
